DT.DOD.DECT.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Total external debt stocks to gross national income.
DT.DOD.DECT.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: External debt stocks

DT.DOD.DSTC.IR.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Short-term debt includes all debt having an original maturity of one year or less and interest in arrears on long-term debt. Total reserves includes gold.
DT.DOD.DSTC.IR.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Short-term debt

DT.DOD.DSTC.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Short-term external debt is defined as debt that has an original maturity of one year or less. Available data permit no distinction between public and private nonguaranteed short-term debt.
DT.DOD.DSTC.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Short-term debt
DT.DOD.DSTC.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.dim: % of exports of goods, services and primary income
DT.DOD.DSTC.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.units: % of exports of goods, services and primary income

DT.DOD.DSTC.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Short-term debt includes all debt having an original maturity of one year or less and interest in arrears on long-term debt. Total external debt is debt owed to nonresidents repayable in currency, goods, or services. Total external debt is the sum of public, publicly guaranteed, and private nonguaranteed long-term debt, use of IMF credit, and short-term debt.
DT.DOD.DSTC.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Short-term debt

DT.DOD.PVLX.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Present value of debt is the sum of short-term external debt plus the discounted sum of total debt service payments due on public, publicly guaranteed, and private nonguaranteed long-term external debt over the life of existing loans. The exports denominator is a three-year average.
DT.DOD.PVLX.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Present value of external debt
DT.DOD.PVLX.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.dim: % of exports of goods, services and income
DT.DOD.PVLX.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.units: % of exports of goods, services and income

DT.DOD.PVLX.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Present value of debt is the sum of short-term external debt plus the discounted sum of total debt service payments due on public, publicly guaranteed, and private nonguaranteed long-term external debt over the life of existing loans. The GNI denominator is a three-year average.
DT.DOD.PVLX.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Present value of external debt

DT.TDS.DECT.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Total debt service to exports of goods, services and primary income. Total debt service is the sum of principal repayments and interest actually paid in currency, goods, or services on long-term debt, interest paid on short-term debt, and repayments (repurchases and charges) to the IMF.
DT.TDS.DECT.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Total debt service
DT.TDS.DECT.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.dim: % of exports of goods, services and primary income
DT.TDS.DECT.EX.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.units: % of exports of goods, services and primary income

DT.TDS.DECT.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Total debt service is the sum of principal repayments and interest actually paid in currency, goods, or services on long-term debt, interest paid on short-term debt, and repayments (repurchases and charges) to the IMF.
DT.TDS.DECT.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Total debt service

DT.TDS.DPPG.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Public and publicly guaranteed debt service is the sum of principal repayments and interest actually paid in currency, goods, or services on long-term obligations of public debtors and long-term private obligations guaranteed by a public entity.
DT.TDS.DPPG.GN.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Public and publicly guaranteed debt service

DT.TDS.DPPG.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Public and publicly guaranteed debt service is the sum of principal repayments and interest actually paid in currency, goods, or services on long-term obligations of public debtors and long-term private obligations guaranteed by a public entity. Exports refer to exports of goods, services, and income.
DT.TDS.DPPG.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Public and publicly guaranteed debt service
DT.TDS.DPPG.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.dim: % of exports of goods, services and primary income
DT.TDS.DPPG.XP.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.units: % of exports of goods, services and primary income

DT.TDS.MLAT.PG.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.def: Multilateral debt service is the repayment of principal and interest to the World Bank, regional development banks, and other multilateral agencies.
DT.TDS.MLAT.PG.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.name: Multilateral debt service
DT.TDS.MLAT.PG.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.dim: % of public and publicly guaranteed debt service
DT.TDS.MLAT.PG.ZS-debtRatiosOtherItems.units: % of public and publicly guaranteed debt service
